phpSysInfo 3.0 RC-5, 2008-06-01
 - Added Estonian, Dutch, Chinese Traditional, Chinese Simplified, Romanian, Brazilian Portuguese, Bulgarian translation
 - Fixed fan speed not showing
 - Updated jquery to 1.2.6
 - Added LFS and HLFS support
 - Fixed bug #1854924: gethostbyaddr can return ip or hostname
 - Possibility to hide network interfaces
 - Temperature format is back
 - Added FR #1799399: standarize units & format for memory / mounts and network
 - Fixed bug #1900449: MBM5 troubles
 - fixed WinNT Swap file detection, if no Swap file is present (inspired by Patch #1902219: No Swapfile)
 - some XHTML fixes
 - language and template change without reloading the entire page, also remember settings in cookie if changed
 - debug output is now back, with nice interface if turned on
 - code cleanup
 - file location reordered (JS)
 - Fixed bug #1928791 php error when an usbdevice has an & in its name
 - WinNT user count reworked
 - updated phpsysinfo.dtd
 - Added a new theme : two.css
 - fix display of filesystem if df returns an error but still has some infos to display returned
 - readd capacity display in the device section
 - readd display of swap devices and restructured memory display
 - fixed division by zero error for swapfiles and also don't show an swapfile entry in the memory usage box when there isn't one
 - count cpu cores when the needed property is available and show this one as cpu count
 - add a redirection to another output of phpsysinfo when javascript is not available (this time it's the raw xml, replaced in the near future by a nicer one)
 - add a system for including plugins (still improvable, but useable)
 - add a /proc/mdstat parser as a plugin (display RAID status)
 - add coretemp driver for hardware monitoring
 
